dct_title_s: Tracing of portion of section no. 6 map showing the survey of lands lying under the waters of the Hudson River and Bay of New York and of lands adjacent thereto, to accompany report to the commissioners to the legislature of the State of New Jersey 1865
dct_description_sm: Tracing of a map designed to accompany a New Jersey State report showing the underwater portions of land adjacent to Jersey City in the Hudson River.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
Map is a tracing; no date provided for when tracing was created. 1865 added as questionable date.
